OL,4,G2300FForensics: Murder Scene
OL,5,     GForensics are called to a
OL,6,     Gterrifying scene at a family
OL,7,     Ghome: a 33-year-old man has been
OL,8,     Gfatally stabbed in his kitchen.
OL,9,     GPolice embark on a huge manhunt
OL,10,     Gto find who is responsible.
OL,11,G0030FMurdered at First Sight
OL,12,     GIn 1989, Mandy Stavik disappears
OL,13,     Gwhile jogging. Her body is found
OL,14,     Gin a river. The case goes cold
OL,15,     Guntil 2013, when DNA evidence
OL,16,     Gconnects local man Timothy Bass
OL,17,     Gto the murder.
